How to play:
At the menu page, player can click on the Intro to understand the premise of the game and watch the storyline unfold. From there, player will be initiated into level one, where they start off in a ship and has to go into the planet in search of one of three quantum stones. They will collect gems as they explore the planet and will need to collect upgrades in order to find the stone. In level 1, they have to find the 'water upgrade' in order to trek water, otherwise they will die in water. Player also has to avoid the roaming robot enemies and falling off platform in order to survive. Once player has collected the first quantum stone, they will move on to Level 2.    

Use WASD or arrow keys to move forward, backward, left, right. 

